                                    <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-chapter-head">[Untitled]</head>
                                    <opener>
                                        <dateline rendition="#right">[<date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-volume-rules" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1873-12-01T23:59:59-04:56" notBefore="1873-01-01T00:00:00-04:56">undated</date>.]</dateline>
                                    </opener>
                                    <p>[<hi rend="italic">N. B.—The summary of this correspondence
                                            is omitted. It mainly relates to the doctrine of
                                            perpetual allegiance, which was abandoned by Congress in
                                            the act of</hi> 1868, (15 <hi rend="italic">Statutes at
                                            Large</hi>, 223,) <hi rend="italic">and which has also
                                            been abandoned by Great Britain and other powers with
                                            whom we have treaties of naturalization</hi>.]</p>
